{"tid":914033,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【8月結婚咁啱三個月】陳凱琳係咪奉子成婚？ 陳爸爸笑晒口：你問番佢啦","createTime":"2018-11-24T01:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T10:33:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"08e784d24373148e96714af90bde8778aa61d7ab","tid":914033,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pBvaeQ7YG6eWha36pXmnVA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/8efff79ab0a68e64f785062a0d3da405\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpBvaeQ7YG6eWha36pXmnVA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F8efff79ab0a68e64f785062a0d3da405&h=9265c59c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一班記者今日去到Grace位於九龍塘嘅娘家等候，即將榮升公公嘅陳凱琳爸爸陳桂祥12點半左右離開大宅時，見到門口有大班記者喺度守候，陳爸爸心情大靚專登行出門口同記者傾偈。大家最關心嘅自然係Grace有咗幾多個月身孕，但係陳爸爸就冇正面回答，只係笑笑話：「呢啲你問番佢啦。」講到會唔會燉啲補品，催谷一向偏瘦嘅囡囡時，陳爸爸話一切會由老婆負責，自己就唔識煮，最多都係同囡囡、女婿出去食飯。至於初為人父人母嘅嘉穎同囡囡有冇好緊張時，陳爸爸話：「都係一般父母心情啦。生仔生女佢哋都冇所謂，平常心。」傾咗分零鐘之後，陳爸爸就入返大宅開車離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%908%E6%9C%88%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%E5%92%81%E5%95%B1%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E3%80%91%E9%99%B3%E5%87%B1%E7%90%B3%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E5%A5%89%E5%AD%90%E6%88%90%E5%A9%9A%EF%BC%9F-%E9%99%B3%E7%88%B8-090928353.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E3%2580%25908%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%25A9%259A%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%2595%25B1%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2587%25B1%25E7%2590%25B3%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2592%25AA%25E5%25A5%2589%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25A9%259A%25EF%25BC%259F-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E7%2588%25B8-090928353.html&d=rDITRtNisujewFGBC%2BDvngdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=65a503ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%908%E6%9C%88%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%E5%92%81%E5%95%B1%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E3%80%91%E9%99%B3%E5%87%B1%E7%90%B3%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E5%A5%89%E5%AD%90%E6%88%90%E5%A9%9A%EF%BC%9F-%E9%99%B3%E7%88%B8-090928353.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20150625/large/25ec2p11e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20150625%2Flarge%2F25ec2p11e1.jpg&h=74ea95fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f33ce6a608aef228152b3469022c485ec4d2c9aa","tid":914033,"uid":102475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:00:16.000Z","msg":"個bb係咪鄭嘉穎架<br />\n生出黎似唔似樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1daa800637c854347dfa7c6aaa70a9a6c2ce457","tid":914033,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:01:38.000Z","msg":"陳凱琳真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646696c3031a3db07eead570fdb5e84ee653a07c","tid":914033,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1daa800637c854347dfa7c6aaa70a9a6c2ce457","tid":914033,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:01:38.000Z","msg":"陳凱琳真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:04:06.000Z","msg":"陳爸認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a12a97a36cf47ee0bc1fae2508251c56e49d8dd","tid":914033,"uid":130950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"646696c3031a3db07eead570fdb5e84ee653a07c","tid":914033,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1daa800637c854347dfa7c6aaa70a9a6c2ce457","tid":914033,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:01:38.000Z","msg":"陳凱琳真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:04:06